Class                  Variables                                                                

Items                  (string) itemID, (string) itemName, (float) itemPrice, (string) itemCategories, (string) itemDescription

Order                  (string) orderId, (string) orderItemId, (string) orderCustomerId, (Timestamp) timestamp

Customer               (string) customerId, (string) name, (float) bill


Datastructures          Details                                                                    Data Structure

Items                   Category decides order, fixed length from file, <key,value> <itemId,info>  -Tree map

Order                   Easy to add, ordered by time stamp (but not unique) so ordered by OrderID  -Tree map

Customer                need to add easily                                                         -a list

end of day report       item, quantity, total, timestamps?, fixed length                           -array?
